{"tid":1149114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不忿女兒天天被欺凌　內地怒父持生果刀衝入小學刺死10歲男生","createTime":"2019-05-11T02:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T15:28:26.000Z","uid":130626,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2557a736797d61964a5154d9ba1a6f91694d44f7","tid":1149114,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"子女被同學欺凌，父母會如何做？江西有一名父親，因女兒長期遭一名男同學欺凌，一怒之下到校以水果刀刺死男生，目前涉事父親遭警方拘捕，案件正在調查中。<br />\n據內地媒體報道，江西上饒市一所小學發生持刀傷人案件，41歲的王姓男子今日(10日)衝入學校，持水果刀刺傷10歲的劉姓學生，當救護人員到場時，傷者已經死亡。據警方調查指，劉姓男生每天都在學校霸凌王姓女生，家長多次勸告都不改，王父一怒之下便到學校傷人。<br />\n有網民事發後在微博公開一段對話截圖，並指在對話中顯示為「何紫璇爸爸」的家長，就是行兇的王姓父親。<br />\n&quot;打何紫璇打的開心嗎？從開學到現在幾乎每日打罵，她在學校很想學習，卻天天被打很是難過。<br />\n作為家長，我也勸說過你，但你還是不聽。<br />\n不知道你家住址，所以只能在校門口等你，會有一個不講理的家長，天天在校門口等你。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n群組其他家長紛紛勸「有事好商量，孩子還小不太懂事，多與家長溝通」等。死者劉姓男生的父母均為醫生，據其父母的同事透露，網上的截圖是劉姓男生所屬的家長群組，但不肯定「何紫璇爸爸」是否涉事的王姓父親。<br />\n該同事又指，劉母平日甚少提及孩子的教育問題，但她性格開朗，為人處事也很好。另一名劉父同事亦指，劉父平日為人很好，事件太突然，受害學生事發前一天，仍在辦公室活蹦亂跳。<br />\n&quot;我們也都聽說了他和同學打架的事，他爸爸也嚴肅教育了他。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n消息曝光後，因欺凌事件引起的刺殺案成為網民討論焦點，不少人認為「父母不教，出來社會自有人替你教」、「唉，父親坐牢，母女倆更難了」、「有的家長真的是溺愛孩子，被欺負的孩子家長相信一開始都是很耐心的去溝通了，這孩子被殺就是被爹媽害的」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2345000/2347982/bully_thumb_20190510_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2345000%2F2347982%2Fbully_thumb_20190510_S_1024.jpg&h=20c0f1b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2347982/%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%BF%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E5%A4%A9%E5%A4%A9%E8%A2%AB%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C%E3%80%80%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%80%92%E7%88%B6%E6%8C%81%E7%94%9F%E6%9E%9C%E5%88%80%E8%A1%9D%E5%85%A5%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%88%BA%E6%AD%BB10%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2347982%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%25BF%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AC%25BA%25E5%2587%258C%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2580%2592%25E7%2588%25B6%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%2588%2580%25E8%25A1%259D%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%2588%25BA%25E6%25AD%25BB10%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=d197e34d\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2347982/%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%BF%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E5%A4%A9%E5%A4%A9%E8%A2%AB%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C%E3%80%80%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%80%92%E7%88%B6%E6%8C%81%E7%94%9F%E6%9E%9C%E5%88%80%E8%A1%9D%E5%85%A5%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%88%BA%E6%AD%BB10%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"d35fedc67fae9da597d0b3b46843de35576c2848","tid":1149114,"uid":82532,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"個女仔就慘啦, 冇咗個老豆, 重唔知使唔使賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8c62bc36ed64bf3c7f1ce8ebb66c07f4f42cf5","tid":1149114,"uid":123738,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T03:02:08.000Z","msg":"支那狗殺得太少了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70dbad72b5da27bfc54a21b7e17b213b47c29b30","tid":1149114,"uid":204929,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T03:04:32.000Z","msg":"以德報德, 以直報怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a80d73bf38a3c0c5043a0e497f733f9a1ac50e","tid":1149114,"uid":39840,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"他還只是個孩子呀<br />\n<br />\n然後...<br />\n<br />\n就死撚左"},{"pid":"b1a9dfbef9e59b2e18bfbe3f298475ed7efaad9e","tid":1149114,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8c8c62bc36ed64bf3c7f1ce8ebb66c07f4f42cf5","tid":1149114,"uid":123738,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T03:02:08.000Z","msg":"支那狗殺得太少了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T03:05:25.000Z","msg":"但係個欺凌者，冇改善自己啲行為喎"},{"pid":"f4e13e01cef7abd8d3d85e3451a617903d013a84","tid":1149114,"uid":237300,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T03:17:30.000Z","msg":"我諗個老豆應該真係無哂方法先會咁，自己唔教就唔好怪個社會幫你教仔，細路識條鐵咩，咪又係老豆老母教出嚟嘅，今次對父母真係害撚死自己個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲害埋人地一家"},{"pid":"3fd408df8352c1096995e46c21cffd4392e6acfd","tid":1149114,"uid":41693,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T03:19:15.000Z","msg":"個老豆係為民除害<br />\n個女就慘 比人恰 又無埋個爸"},{"pid":"55202f858c0c4d2e4cdad9fb83c53edb020bc512","tid":1149114,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70dbad72b5da27bfc54a21b7e17b213b47c29b30","tid":1149114,"uid":204929,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T03:04:32.000Z","msg":"以德報德, 以直報怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a320293088750278a843836946a192996599ff","tid":1149114,"uid":182701,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T08:29:27.000Z","msg":"「何紫璇爸爸」的家長，就是行兇的王姓父親。<br />\n點解佢個女唔係跟佢姓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016f89b6ec070246f7c03a470148431de7937237","tid":1149114,"uid":204929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T12:51:42.000Z","msg":"黑心啲講句， 如果佢冇死， 佢大個一定係殺人犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 所以依家個欺凌者死就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa16503501ac8a037d2609c2cc8097e8490c4cf","tid":1149114,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:09:09.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"282329e2c34a55874d6673333aa68421d84031cd","tid":1149114,"uid":23162,"like":3,"dislike"